Package system

package system
Contains system-level classes and configuration for the application.

This package includes classes that manage the overall system settings, configuration, and integration of different application components. It may also include the initialization of external resources or APIs, application startup routines, and global settings.

Key classes in this package:

  • CSVReader - read in CSV data
  • CSVWriter - function to write data into csv file
  • HMS - run main system
  • InventoryParser - to parse and construct the Inventory object
  • PatientParser - to parse and construct the Patient object
  • SessionManager - manage session
  • StaffParser - to parse and construct the User object
  • SystemManager - handle the operation of system
  • Writer - handle the writing of data into different file

Since:
1.0
Author:
Chong Jia Chern
